{"tid":484894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【非政治正確、純技術分析】性侵案事隔多年先講　無論係真定假，都已經輸左","createTime":"2017-11-30T12:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T14:31:01.000Z","uid":88713,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7ee5d45f1c583514fe5319f07b0cd568464620","tid":484894,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"撇除政治正確，也先不論呂麗瑤事件的真確性，純粹從操作角度分析<br />\n<br />\n一個性侵受害人，事隔多年以後公開遭遇，固然勇氣可嘉。只不過，受到性侵後不立即報警，待證據全失後才現身說法，只會令自己陷於極尷尬的境地。<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會覺得，受到性侵後會不知所措、心情未平伏，或者甚至不知道如何保障自己的權益。那學校、家長就需要教育孩子，遇到不幸事件時如何最好的保障自己，如何處理就靠受害人自行決定。但至少，事隔多年才公開並非最好的方法。<br />\n<br />\n這世界上，真偽難辨的指控太多，而指控本身已是影響別人聲譽，尤其當受害者是女性或是兒童時，被指控者必定身敗名裂。但如果拿不出確切證據，有或者無發生，就只有當事人真正知道（當然，有個別女權分子是認為對男人的性侵指控是應該寧枉勿縱的，但這是腦殘級別故不足論*註1）<br />\n<br />\n即使事件屬真，報警了，將加害者告上法庭了，法官唯一可以信納的「證據」，理論上就只剩下當事人的片面之詞。到時告不入，又話法律不公正；告得入，又難免令人覺得片面之詞足以入罪，法律偏袒女性。那為何一開始就不拿出最有力的證據指控對方呢？<br />\n<br />\n須知道，有關性侵的法例，無論理論上抑或執行上，先天上都是保護女性，而假定男人是加害者。即使發現是指控屬假，誣告者卻不須受到等同的代價（註2）。<br />\n<br />\n性侵摧毀受害人的一生，誣告又何嘗不是。<br />\n<br />\n註1：女權分子偉論<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SchoolForLeftard/photos/a.136990520361217.1073741828.132715444122058/148318839228385/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSchoolForLeftard%2Fphotos%2Fa.136990520361217.1073741828.132715444122058%2F148318839228385%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0ji8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4e5454eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SchoolForLeftard/photos/a.136990520361217.1073741828.132715444122058/148318839228385/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195876&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0ji8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=79f7c40e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195876&h=87fbafa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195876</a><br />\n（註2：30歲女報復男方中出即飛，虛報強姦，但留下證據被發現報假案，最後只判社會服務令）"},{"pid":"252094c978c81e78e3fc30ca35f81dd48409b817","tid":484894,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"根本告唔到，日期時間都無，告條毛咩"},{"pid":"967fbe3623fe34298c492ddffd07119263e80244","tid":484894,"uid":88713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本告唔到，日期時間都無，告條毛咩</blockquote><br />\n唔告仲大鑊，個男方連有冇做過都查唔到，但就白白捱左一刀，工又冇埋，朵又臭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa9de5a9a8914374fccd3ded581de9493bc7876","tid":484894,"uid":88713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:45:25.000Z","msg":"同場加映：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A9%9A%E4%BA%8B%E6%92%BBq%E5%A5%B3%E7%BF%BB%E8%88%8A%E8%B3%AC%E7%88%8613%E6%AD%B2%E7%8D%BB%E5%88%9D%E5%A4%9C-%E6%82%94%E5%A9%9A%E7%94%B7%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA-083555657.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A9%259A%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2592%25BBq%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%2588%258A%25E8%25B3%25AC%25E7%2588%258613%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%258D%25BB%25E5%2588%259D%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E6%2582%2594%25E5%25A9%259A%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA-083555657.html&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0ji8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=deef4ac6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A9%9A%E4%BA%8B%E6%92%BBq%E5%A5%B3%E7%BF%BB%E8%88%8A%E8%B3%AC%E7%88%8613%E6%AD%B2%E7%8D%BB%E5%88%9D%E5%A4%9C-%E6%82%94%E5%A9%9A%E7%94%B7%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA-083555657.html</a>"},{"pid":"93ac4a9b886ac400ce0701dda461fcf6f8e1547a","tid":484894,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnai